message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with audio signal processing and separation. Other likely categories could be cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper proposes a deep learning-based approach, cs.SI (sound and music computing) as the paper deals with singing voice separation, cs.CV (computer vision) as the paper uses a sparse transformation step, and cs.NE (neural and evolutionary computing) as the paper proposes a recurrent inference algorithm.
